 and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average price methodology. The rate is determined by the premium/discount between the perpetual contract price and the underlying spot price, adjusted for market sentiment indicators. Long positions pay short positions when funding is positive, while shorts pay longs when negative, with payments automatically processed at settlement times."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
